}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/?p=227985\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:442:\"Twenty Twenty is the newest theme released with WordPress version 5.3. I tested this new theme with Paid Memberships Pro and believe it is a strong choice for anyone looking to start a membership site on WordPress. Watch the video below to see the theme working together with PMPro. The article include screenshots of the <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/twenty-twenty-theme-wordpress-membership-site/\" rel=\"nofollow\">(more...)</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Kimberly Coleman\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5993:\"<div class=\"lead\"><p>Twenty Twenty is the newest theme <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2019/11/kirk/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">released with WordPress version 5.3</a>. I tested this new theme with Paid Memberships Pro and believe it is a strong choice for anyone looking to start a membership site on WordPress.</p>\n<p>Watch the video below to see the theme working together with PMPro. The article include screenshots of the frontend theme experience as well as a block of custom CSS you can use to make this plugin and theme combo even tighter.</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"744\" height=\"419\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xdk_uATpnGA\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe><br />\n</div><hr /></p>\n<h2>Screenshots of Various Plugin Pages</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels-3col-1024x647.jpg\" alt=\"Membership Advanced Levels Shortcode - Twenty Twenty Theme\" width=\"744\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-228057\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels-3col-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels-3col-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels-3col.jpg 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" /><em class=\"muted\">Membership Levels Page using the <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/pmpro-advanced-levels-shortcode/\">Advanced Levels Page Shortcode Add On</a></em></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels-1024x647.jpg\" alt=\"Membership Levels - Twenty Twenty Theme\" width=\"744\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-228058\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-levels.jpg 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" /><em class=\"muted\">Membership Levels default Page</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-account-1024x647.jpg\" alt=\"Membership Account - Twenty Twenty Theme\" width=\"744\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-228053\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-account-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-account-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-account.jpg 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" /><em class=\"muted\">Membership Account Page</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-billing-1024x647.jpg\" alt=\"Membership Billing - Twenty Twenty Theme\" width=\"744\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-228054\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-billing-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-billing-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-billing.jpg 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" /><em class=\"muted\">Membership Billing Page</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-checkout-1024x647.jpg\" alt=\"Membership Checkout - Twenty Twenty Theme\" width=\"744\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-228055\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-checkout-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-checkout-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-checkout.jpg 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" /><em class=\"muted\">Membership Checkout Page</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-invoice-1024x647.jpg\" alt=\"Membership Invoice - Twenty Twenty Theme\" width=\"744\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-228056\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-invoice-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-invoice-300x189.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/twenty-twenty-membership-invoice.jpg 1140w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\" /><em class=\"muted\">Membership Invoice Page</em></p>\n<hr id=\"css\" />\n<h2>Recommended Custom CSS</h2>\n<p>We do our best to allow the frontend pages for Paid Memberships Pro to inherit your theme&#8217;s appearance. Sometimes a few lines of CSS are needed to really tighten up the appearance and make all frontend plugin pages truly reflect your theme designer&#8217;s goals for content, be it for button appearance, dividers, content width, and more.</p>\n<p>This custom CSS can be placed in a <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/enqueue-a-customizations-stylesheet-in-your-pmpro-customizations-plugin/\">stylesheet for PMPro Customizations</a> or pasted directly into the Appearance > Customize > Additional CSS field. You can also include this CSS in your child theme&#8217;s <code>style.css</code> file if you are using a child theme for Twenty Twenty.</p>\n<p>View the code on <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/kimcoleman/6cd4c74865ae6625264277790ff944aa\">Gist</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/twenty-twenty-theme-wordpress-membership-site/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attr